This is really hard to write but Fux. Rip To My BDay Twin.. 🥺😭 
Ain’t no Fuxin way, I Don’t Believe this for one moment. But I digress 🥺😡🤬.. 
This man was a Beam of Light and has been there for me as a friend and a Teacher since 2005. For almost 20 years this man would reach out on our Bday no matter where he was in the world. Man Sept 29th will never feel the same. You where so Special my friend. Rest Well Bro and know we got you and your fam for life. Heaven is Lucky to have you. Your sprit will forever be protected with Prayer! Love you bro.
🥺Missing You Twin.. #familia #bdaytwins
